frames.caption: A majestic whale breaches the surface of the icy ocean, towering over a group of penguins gathered on a small ice floe. The scene captures the awe-inspiring scale of the whale against the serene backdrop of icebergs and clear blue skies.
frames.description: The image depicts a dramatic encounter in a polar region, where a whale emerges from the water near a group of penguins. The setting is a cold, icy landscape with floating ice and distant icebergs under a bright, clear sky.
